Package it.polimi.ingsw.gc03.view.ui.events

Enum Class EventType

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<EventType>
it.polimi.ingsw.gc03.view.ui.events.EventType
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<EventType>, Constable
public enum EventType extends Enum<EventType>
Enumeration of event types used in the game. This enum defines the various types of events that can occur during the game's lifecycle.
